<h2><strong>CADmeister 2020 Version Upgrade (PRESS)</strong><br>&nbsp;</h2><h3><strong>&bull; DIE-LAYOUT/3DDL&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_0.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>1.&nbsp;Set &amp; Edit Various Types of Data for 3DDL　</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Management function has been added to control various information settings.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>2.&nbsp;3DDL Layout Consideration</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Transport Considerations function has been added to ExamineLayout command.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>3.&nbsp;Die Structure ASSY Output for 3DDL</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released the functions to output consideration results data into an ASSY structure</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>4.&nbsp;Coordinate System Definition Command Improvement</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Added standard axis revolves option in the order of axis revolution.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_4.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>5.&nbsp;&ldquo;Pierce Automatic Placement&rdquo; Command for Support Design Changed</strong></h4><p>- &nbsp;Released an add-on function to detect and compare before &amp; after changing data</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_5.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;PRESS&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>6.&nbsp;Product Hole Simplified Measurement for &ldquo;Pierce Auto Placement&rdquo; Command</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released an add-on function to support a case where a hole diameter cannot be recognized as PIERCE diameter.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_6.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;FORM-EX&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>7. &nbsp;Global Deformation / Variable Amount Incorporated Deform</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Renewed functions of &ldquo;CAE_Twist&rdquo; command and &ldquo;Twist&rdquo; command have been released.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_7.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>8.&nbsp;&ldquo;EnterDisplacementFile&amp;Deform&rdquo; Command</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Symmetrical deformation is now enabled through the use of asymmetrical analysis data.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_8.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull;&nbsp;Easy_Modeling&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>9.&nbsp;&ldquo;2StepExtendedSurface&rdquo; Command</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released efficient and user-friendly function to extend surfaces in two stages.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_9.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>10.&nbsp;Ribbon Surface</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released an add-on function to adjust angle of Upper Blade Surface.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_10.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 